text: DXAQ-TV, channel 43, is a religious television station owned by Sonshine Media Network International (SMNI). Its studios are located at the Kingdom of Jesus Christ compound, Philippine-Japan Friendship Highway, Sasa, Davao City and transmitter are located at Shrine Hills, Matina, Davao City. DXAQ-TV now broadcasts on 24 hours daily, 365 days a year non stop operation. == Other websites == * SMNI.com Category:Filipino television stations Category:2003 establishments in Asia Category:2000s establishments in the Philippines
